ABOUT
Cucu's Nest Bar
Visiting Miami or living here? Cucu's Nest bar is incredibly friendly, fun place to visit. Delicious food, special drinks, great atmosphere and incredible people is what describes us!
​
Come here, make new friends, have few drinks and make new warm memories.
​
This is the ideal weekend activity because of the vibrant energy and exceptional atmosphere. It goes without saying that a night spent here, at one of the best party venues, will be special and unforgettable.
GET DIRECTIONS
About
DJ and Jukebox
Every type of bar is given a boost of style and good times whenever there is a jukebox present.
Few experiences in life are more satisfying than entering a bar, approaching the jukebox, and selecting the ideal song. You reach a unique state of extreme badassness when you compete with your friends using your best tracks on a jukebox that includes a wide variety of classic albums, obscure indie bands, and fans-only favorites, especially when you can do that on a digital  jukebox.
​
Want to party and enjoy DJ music? Follow
our Instagram account
not to miss new DJ announcements.
Story
Cucu's Nest Bar STORY
Cucu's Nest Bar has a history back to early 2000s when it was a hot spot and a dive bar for locals. Little by little it was turning to a  favorite place among tourists who were coming back to the bar their every visit to Miami.
​
Caring the best warm  memories from making friends during happy hour drink, parties till 5 a.m. with karaoke, pool and hot outgoing bartenders, Cucu's Nest Bar now reopened on South Beach!
​
